**Professional Examples** ğŸ’¼:  
- **Spotify Wrapped**: Har saal Spotify AI ka use karta hai jo aapke music taste ke base par **personalized playlist covers** aur visuals banata hai. Agar aapko hip-hop pasand hai, to ek graffiti-style cover milega; agar classical, to violin wala design! ğŸ§  
- **Adobe Sensei**: Photoshop mein AI low-quality images ko high-quality banata hai ya damaged photos ke missing parts repair karta hai (jaise, ek purani tasveer ka background fix karna). ğŸ–Œï¸  

